:"The Spider","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3404,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3404.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3404.mp3"],"text":"وَمَا هَٰذِهِ ٱلْحَيَوٰةُ ٱلدُّنْيَآ إِلَّا لَهْوٌۭ وَلَعِبٌۭ ۚ وَإِنَّ ٱلدَّارَ ٱلْءَاخِرَةَ لَهِىَ ٱلْحَيَوَانُ ۚ لَوْ كَانُوا۟ يَعْلَمُونَ","numberInSurah":64,"juz":21,"manzil":5,"page":404,"ruku":348,"hizbQuarter":161,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":29,"name":"سُورَةُ العَنكَبُوتِ","englishName":"Al-Ankaboot","englishNameTranslation":"The Spider","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3405,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3405.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3405.mp3"],"text":"فَإِذَا رَكِبُوا۟ فِى ٱلْفُلْكِ دَعَوُا۟ ٱللَّهَ مُخْلِصِينَ لَهُ ٱلدِّينَ فَلَمَّا نَجَّىٰهُمْ إِلَى ٱلْبَرِّ إِذَا هُمْ يُشْرِكُونَ","numberInSurah":65,"juz":21,"manzil":5,"page":404,"ruku":348,"hizbQuarter":161,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":29,"name":"سُورَةُ العَنكَبُوتِ","englishName":"Al-Ankaboot","englishNameTranslation":"The Spider","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3406,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3406.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3406.mp3"],"text":"لِيَكْفُرُوا۟ بِمَآ ءَاتَيْنَٰهُمْ وَلِيَتَمَتَّعُوا۟ ۖ فَسَوْفَ يَعْلَمُونَ","numberInSurah":66,"juz":21,"manzil":5,"page":404,"ruku":348,"hizbQuarter":161,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":29,"name":"سُورَةُ العَنكَبُوتِ","englishName":"Al-Ankaboot","englishNameTranslation":"The Spider","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3407,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3407.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3407.mp3"],"text":"أَوَلَمْ يَرَوْا۟ أَنَّا جَعَلْنَا حَرَمًا ءَامِنًۭا وَيُتَخَطَّفُ ٱلنَّاسُ مِنْ حَوْلِهِمْ ۚ أَفَبِٱلْبَٰطِلِ يُؤْمِنُونَ وَبِنِعْمَةِ ٱللَّهِ يَكْفُرُونَ","numb